    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolutely pristine, showroom condition. The exterior paint retains a mirror-like finish with zero scratches or dings, and the interior is spotless, still smelling fresh. Mechanically, it performs flawlessly, providing a smooth and powerful driving experience as if it just rolled off the assembly line. Every feature and electronic component works perfectly, making this a rare find for a discerning buyer seeking a like-new vehicle.",
